# identifiers

**Instance Property**

A list of unique identifiers corresponding to detected feature points.

## Declaration

```swift
@nonobjc var identifiers: [UInt64] { get }
```

## Discussion

Each identifier in this list corresponds to the point vector at the same index in the [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARPointCloud/points-4vkif] array.

## Identifying Feature Points

- **points**: The list of detected points.
